summary - information on overriding and adding help text
help \
    The help text is contained in the lexa format file called `lx.help.lexa`.\
    This file, and it's included sub-files, provide the text for the lx help\
    system. Subjects can be nested by key name, and each subject key has at \
    least two items; `summary` and `help`.

